ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectActs of the Second Extraordinary Congress of the Universal Postal Union
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to delegate authority to represent, to take part in deliberations, to vote and to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the ACTS OF THE SECOND EXTRAORDINARY CONGRESS OF THE UNIVERSAL POSTAL UNION, to be held in Addis Ababa from September 3 to 7, 2018.
